node.text:
I MISS IKEA!! Simple lunch 🙂 Blanched some spinach and made some gravy to go along with the pan fried salmon, boiled meatballs and steamed mashed potato. Bought the frozen salmon, beef meatballs and mashed potato from #Ikea before the start of #circuitbreaker period 
#ikea #homemadelovers #hlfunbake #lightmeal #onedishmeal #foodinsing #culinaryarts #foodphotography #onmytable #homecooking #instayum #instagram #circuitbreakersg
Looked exactly like what you get from ikea👍💕💕
